FlowState Autonomous Wealth Optimization Platform - UI Build Complete

COMPLETED FEATURES:
===================

1. Main Dashboard (app/page.tsx)
   - Dark mode theme with emerald green accents (#10B981)
   - Sticky header with FlowState branding
   - Three metric tiles: Surplus Capital, Burn Rate, Potential Yield
   - "Analyze My Finances" primary CTA with loading states
   - Recommendation cards with reasoning manifests (Insight → Benefit)
   - Support for 3 recommendation types:
     * Idle Money Sweep (money market funds)
     * Subscription Vampire Detection (unused subscriptions)
     * Anomaly Alerts (duplicate charges/refunds)
   - Collapsible transaction sidebar with flagged items
   - Confirmation dialog before executing actions
   - Success/error messaging (auto-dismiss after 5s)
   - Real AI agent integration via callAIAgent()

2. Settings Page (app/settings/page.tsx)
   - Risk profile selector (Conservative vs Aggressive)
   - Detailed comparison of risk profiles
   - Idle money alert threshold slider (5-50%)
   - Auto-execute toggle for low-risk moves
   - Notification preferences for 4 types:
     * Idle Money Opportunities
     * Subscription Alerts
     * Anomaly Alerts
     * Weekly Financial Report
   - LocalStorage persistence
   - Save confirmation

3. Agent Integration
   - Wealth Architect Manager: 698586be382ef8715224cf22
   - Data Cruncher Agent: 69858660382ef8715224cf1d
   - Market Strategist Agent: 6985867f49f279d47448a5c3
   - Executioner Agent: 698586981caa4e686dd66dba
   - Smart response parsing with fallback to defaults
   - Loading states during agent calls
   - Error handling with user-friendly messages

4. Design System (Per PRD)
   - 8pt grid system
   - Dark mode: slate-950/900 backgrounds
   - Emerald green (#10B981) for positive actions
   - Typography: Bold numbers for financial figures
   - Progress rings for burn rate visualization
   - Priority badges (high/medium/low)
   - Status badges (completed/flagged)
   - Responsive design with Tailwind CSS

5. User Journey
   ✓ Dashboard loads → Zero state with CTA
   ✓ Click "Analyze My Finances" → Loading spinner
   ✓ Agent response parsed → Cards populate
   ✓ Review reasoning manifest → Insight → Benefit
   ✓ Click "Execute" → Confirmation modal
   ✓ Confirm → Executioner agent called
   ✓ Success → Card updates to "Completed" state
   ✓ Metrics update in real-time

TECHNICAL IMPLEMENTATION:
=========================

- React hooks for state management
